Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.64,Episode-Title - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(442,1)}Episode 9\N"Moon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:10.77,Text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,To: Yukinari\NSubject: Hinode-hama today \NGood weather all day.\NIn front of the gelato store.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:17.11,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What am I writing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:32.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Just why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.88,Sign,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Message from Sacchan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,For tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.94,Text - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,From: Sacchan\NSubject: For tomorrow\N"Ten Nights of Dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Ten Nights of Dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:53.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.94,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.78,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.90,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.20,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:12.17,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name of a novel, isn't it? \NBy Soseki Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.12,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the shelf at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.78,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.09,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's an exam question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.57,Book Cover,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Issen Ichibyou Monogatari
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.57,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell your boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.70,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,that you're coming home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:42.78,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.63,Book Cover - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Soseki Natsume\NTen Nights of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.71,Text - Copy - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Inbox\NYanagi\NHinode-hama today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.66,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What did Touko see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.82,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.15,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear the fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:27.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Navel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:28.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.77,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.78,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt your running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.28,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.18,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:56.39,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, we promised to go shopping together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.98,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Come over tomorrow if you have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.48,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.14,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Onee-chan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.43,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.36,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.41,Italics,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened recently, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.30,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kakeru, what are you\Ngoing to do after you graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.25,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.46,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You sure haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:30.33,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should start\Nthinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.30,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.38,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You should find a stable job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.66,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'm in a position to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.14,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your father and I both knew what we wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,to be ever since we were little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.46,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the case for you though, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.66,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mom wouldn't stay put, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.12,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're going overseas next, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.82,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'll be gone for a while this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.83,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.49,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.25,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That boy said he liked it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.63,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought he found something he wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.71,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,His girlfriend, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:08.40,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.79,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If you come back again\Nduring the summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.11,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't get in their way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.25,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness is partly thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.35,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If he asked me, I'd support\Nhim with everything I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.27,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're really just lonely, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.64,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:28.22,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.74,Text - Copy - Copy (2),Text,0000,0000,0000,,To: Yukinari\NSubject: Hinode-hama today\NGood weather today.\NHinode Bridge, futon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.00,Sign,Text,0000,0000,0000,,New message
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:51.71,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.21,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, it's Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.28,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.08,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.35,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.94,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Touko gave me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.21,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,So, I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.05,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of clothes\N that I can't wear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.44,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to try them \Non before we go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.13,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.49,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect. So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.21,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not that skirt. Something more frilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.93,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yanagi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.24,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something you want to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.23,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,About Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.30,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you've been wanting\Nto ask since yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.63,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.51,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.31,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not a broken heart, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.09,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.52,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think I know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.83,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,any more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.34,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:52.33,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.65,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,have a one-sided promise \Nto ask someone who probably
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:56.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,knows a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.80,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,"One-sided"? That's not exactly\N a "promise," then, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.54,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:03.89,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.63,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko's really important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:10.88,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,This is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.23,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.05,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.88,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.78,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's a hand-me-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.84,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy. Are you sure, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.85,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wear it anymore, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:27.38,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's an outfit Yuki complimented me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.44,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't \Nremember anymore, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.31,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.26,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.98,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're already cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.03,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.40,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.88,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pulling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.04,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.08,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.11,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:52.13,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi-san gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yanagi-san's got such good taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.77,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,...a bit too tight around the waist for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.74,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been doing lately, Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.77,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing speed sketches and life drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.91,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky you have no written exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:13.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.25,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.14,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Sacchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.71,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,We ended up talking a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:27.19,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,about Onee-chan today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.24,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan was being nice to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.08,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,because you're so worried about your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.65,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.63,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, how were the tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.42,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get the results for at least a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.99,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:41.33,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:43.03,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.19,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to that place we promised to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.93,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The place we promised to go before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:51.81,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:58.11,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet tomorrow at Kirinkan at four?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.40,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.87,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.35,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.07,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.94,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'll make dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.79,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.68,Text - Copy - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,New camping techniques\NFrom: Sacchan\NSubject: For tomorrow\NPlease come to Kirinkan tomorrow at four.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.47,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Meijinden"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Kirinkan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,For tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.94,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There's so many things I want to say but can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.82,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The place we promised to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.72,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.99,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't listening to your monologue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.58,Text - Copy - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,To: Yukinari\NSubject: Hinode-hama today\NCumulonimbus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.92,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What are you being so fidgety about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.70,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you expecting a message from your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.72,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.63,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Just call her. Don't worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:10.85,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Not that we won't be listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.59,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Lights out, unless you want your precious message deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.59,Main,ABC,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:15.94,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,I'm turning it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:16.73,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.66,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.25,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He can delete the email,\Nbut he can't delete love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.41,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.83,Sign,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Unread emails
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:34.58,Text - Copy - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi\NHinode-hama today\NClear skies all day.\NIn front of the gelato store.\NBlacks: 1 Whites: 2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.58,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Blacks: 1, Whites: 2."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.51,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Clear skies today."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.54,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"A futon on Hinode Bridge."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.97,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Cumulonimbus. Strong winds."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.47,Text - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cumulonimbus.\NStrong winds. \NHigh tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.92,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"High tides."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.99,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Just hear me out as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.53,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the art room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'll see this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:27.61,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Can you talk about what \Nyou saw at the art room now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.24,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:33.31,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We might learn something \Nabout the fragments if we go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:38.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to know about\N the fragments of the future that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:42.11,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough\N information about the fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.44,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.35,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't discussed it enough either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.03,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to create the same conditions in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.23,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.74,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what it's about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.83,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I saw snow. When we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It was a world of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.71,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Snow everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never seen anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.38,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.48,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:09.85,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.64,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to \Nhear the fragments lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.10,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I may never hear them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.72,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Taniguchi broke\N39 minutes in the 10,000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.98,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? He just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.93,Text - Copy - Copy (2),Text,0000,0000,0000,,From: Yanagi\NSubject: Hinode-hama today\NClear skies today.\NThe Sea of Japan is \Nbreezy during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.33,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Clear skies," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.28,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.86,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:17.84,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.64,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry they're so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.13,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,They made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:23.16,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.29,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,blinding right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.92,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining over here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.07,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.19,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,My knees...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.76,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,They hurt a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.38,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I told Coach too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.08,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:43.73,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I might have rushed it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:48.32,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of things happened this summer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.75,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Summer is always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:54.94,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds of things \Nhappen during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.46,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.70,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.94,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Our parents got remarried\N in summer as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.42,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted only a modest wedding, \Nsince they'd both been married before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.84,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:08.29,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom changed her wedding outfit three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.57,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.38,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I feel relaxed when I talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. When are you coming home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.91,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, when does camp end again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.16,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.58,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We might be done tomorrow, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.44,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Same old you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:32.69,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.32,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you at Hinode-hama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.15,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get invited, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You too? By Sacchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.78,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.41,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.25,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.82,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:31.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:32.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.67,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:38.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can I expect an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.18,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:44.01,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where you wanted to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:45.27,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.63,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,One of your pictures was\Nput on display here, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.07,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:56.37,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the Hinode-hama\Nbreakwaters from here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.20,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a swallow nest on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.23,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:09.91,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,it's still a lot more wonderful that\N you've been living here all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.05,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.97,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be here after closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.94,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stay here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.64,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What you need "for tomorrow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.28,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,About this city, or about Yana-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,or about Yuki-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:57.88,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,or Hiro-kun, or Sacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.59,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I don't know what's about to happen next,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.09,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.66,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you can vaguely\N see the shadow of the moon today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.72,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's called earthshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:13.73,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that because the earth\N is reflecting the sun's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So we came here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.28,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,today to see the moon, Sacchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:21.95,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:23.91,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:28.07,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,This time of the year, this Kirinkan—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.22,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It becomes a totally different place,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.54,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,depending on the season and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:37.47,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I could come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.08,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,to my special place,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.68,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,with you two, Touko-chan and Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.68,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,This is your promised place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Your special place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.68,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:55.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, thanks for bringing me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.36,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's pretty though, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0} I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it becomes a confession\N when you say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.52,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,A confession?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I looked it up recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:13.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,When Soseki Natsume was an English teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:16.71,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,that's how he taught how to translate "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:19.76,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Soseki Natsume? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.33,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:24.42,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.20,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:29.84,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's, like, more tasteful that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:32.31,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That would really get your feelings across?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.83,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:38.98,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-san was a romantic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:42.41,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:47.66,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,And those are my lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.26,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't kept it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:33.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Touko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:36.14,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been protecting Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:38.52,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko Fukami, I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.52,Episode-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10\N"Jonathan"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.52,Episode-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,
